metadata.description:
eyes showed moved color, and said: "Ming brother, there was really a pulse tester tested, you inherited your father's blood?"



"Yes, Yao 'er, so your man will be a strong one in the future." Lu Ming's face shows a confident smile.



Lu Yao smiled and lifted the glass on the stone table. In the glass was the famous orchid wine with blood tongue, emitting a faint fragrance.
